description:
Sidenote: I think I was high off dentist druggery in that bathroom. Unsure.

Just a quick update of where I've been. I just want to thank you guys so much for your support. Not going to get super in detail about it right now, but I'll just say my family hasn't been able to afford for me to go to an orthodontist in a long time. But thanks to you Samurai, I can finally after YEARS get my dentistry taken care of. Once again, you guys are the best.

In Chicago but still going to try and make a video for tomorrow.
